data.description: Unlock the full potential of this 5.27-acre paradise, where your dreams of rural living become a reality while you are still close to major shoppes and A+ rated schools. Nestled in a serene environment and zoned for agriculture, this property is your canvas for building the life you've always envisioned. With ample space and zoning that welcomes your imagination, you have the perfect opportunity to design and construct the custom home of your dreams. Currently on the property, 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom main home(needs TLC) and a detached 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom efficiency, and a generous detached garage invites you to indulge your hobbies and store your vehicles, making this property ideal for the avid tinkerer or collector. Approximately 2 acres of this land are currently utilized as a nursery Enjoy the convenience of public sewer access and dependable Florida Power & Light (FPL) service, ensuring that your rural oasis comes with the modern amenities you need. While you relish the peaceful countryside, essential amenities, schools, shopping, and major transportation routes are just a stone's throw away. Imagine waking up each day to the beauty of your own piece of paradise. Whether you're an aspiring farmer, nature enthusiast, or simply seeking refuge from the city, this property promises boundless opportunities. Your dream life begins here. Opportunities like this are rare. Don't let this chance slip away.
